When I watch his performance videos and dance practice videos, I am amazed by his vocal skills and dance choreography synchronization. His dancing skills and vocal skills are phenomenal, amazing and inspiring to watch. Out of all the solo kpop artists, he stands out from the crowd for his dynamic originality.  I would love to attend a world tour performance. I hope he would consider performing at the PNC Bank Arts Center Holmdel, NJ USA.

He's thriving in various fields & not just in music.
May he continue to live a beautiful, wonderful life full of good health, happiness, love, & many blessings.
